      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SMOOTH BLAST (1) had the drop on the pace early but forged to the lead on the bend and drew clear to score (28.80) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 498m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Can make it back-to-back wins. I'M FREE (6) is on a hot streak recording a 29.06 win over 498m at this track last start following on from a convincing 21.69 victory at this track over 380m the start prior. Flying lately and looks a key chance on that form. TOTAL FRANKY (2) is a talented type who boasts a strong winning strike-rate at this distance. Has been on speed to score at his last couple of runs. Scored latest at this track in a handy 28.76. Likely to be in the finish. TIPSY TESS (8) was well supported last time but could only manage second (29.00), beaten 2.75 lengths. Deserves a win and gets her chance.",
